112
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:26,000
**Kim Eo-jun:** Consecutive blows.

113
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:45,800
**Cho Yoon-beom:** He had many older brothers. Uniquely, he was close to his sisters-in-law. One of them also died suddenly. The woman he liked later became his third sister-in-law. She married his brother. That brother died later. His close sister-in-law died too. His personality completely changed then.

114
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:52,400
**Kim Eo-jun:** He must have felt a huge sense of loss.

115
