119
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:49,200
**Cho Yoon-beom:** He didn't bond well because she was very ill when he was 2 or 3, so he was raised in another house. He grew up at a local grocery store during his infancy, so he was separated from his mother and had little bond with her.

120
00:14:47,000 --> 00:15:01,400
**Kim Eo-jun:** When everyone you bonded with dies at once, your emotional growth can stop at that moment. You stop growing and stay there. Some people live their whole lives like that, like at age 15.

121
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:06,400
**Cho Yoon-beom:** You could say he stopped there. He changed that much. He started drinking heavily.

122
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:13,200
**Kim Eo-jun:** Well, one can drink. Some people even become president after drinking.

123
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:19,000
